---
version: 1
op: model.predict_next
description: predict the top 3 likely follow-up queries given recent session activity
max_output_tokens: 100
vars: [recent_queries, current]
---
You predict what the user will ask next. Given recent queries from this session, output the top 3 most likely follow-up queries.

Recent queries (most recent last):
{{.recent_queries}}

Current query: {{.current}}

Output ONLY a JSON object — no prose, no markdown fence. Predictions should be specific (a coder might actually type them), not generic. Each ≤10 words.

{"predictions": ["query 1", "query 2", "query 3"]}

Example: {"predictions":["how do refresh tokens work","what is the JWT signing algorithm","where is the auth middleware"]}
